Level caps (like DMG cap) would be best.. After 50, those resists make a bit of sense. At level 13, they do not..<br>
<br>
And as for the Enchanter.. I agree 100%. Tash just doesn't do the trick at that level, considering how poorly enchanters nuke vs. other casting classes. <br>
